00:09:28.260 --> 00:09:33.540
learn how to find trusty sources of information;
discover how media and your mind interact;

00:09:33.540 --> 00:09:36.900
and explore creating media and the
responsibilities that come with it.

00:09:36.900 --> 00:09:41.760
In the second half of the course we’ll use this
theory to look at how media works in the world:

00:09:41.760 --> 00:09:45.600
we’ll discover how it’s regulated (the
