00:09:45.600 --> 00:09:50.720
the dark side of the media, like propaganda and
misinformation; the lure of advertising;

00:09:50.720 --> 00:09:56.440
how the big tech companies are changing
the media landscape; plus we’ll take a look at
where the field is headed.

00:09:56.440 --> 00:10:04.400
Throughout the course, we’ll return to the core
principles of media literacy – to build a framework with
which to approach our everyday, media-filled lives.

